        <h1 class="page-title">Text field</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          The Text Input is a form control component that allows users to enter and edit single-line text. It provides labels, placeholder text, prefix/suffix elements, helper text, character counters, validation states, and clear functionality.
        </p>
