          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #ea580c);">9</span><div><strong>Clear Button</strong><span>An "X" icon to clear the input field content.</span></div></div>
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #ea580c);">10</span><div><strong>Helper Icon</strong><span>Small icon that accompanies the helper text.</span></div></div>
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #ea580c);">11</span><div><strong>Helper Text</strong><span>Supporting text providing context, validation messages, or formatting guidance.</span></div></div>
