          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">The Text Input component fully supports right-to-left (RTL) layouts for Arabic, Hebrew, and other RTL languages.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li><strong>Layout mirrored:</strong> The entire input layout mirrors horizontally. Label moves to the right, input field aligns accordingly.</li>
            <li><strong>Prefix/suffix swap:</strong> Prefix elements appear on the right side and suffix elements on the left side in RTL mode.</li>
            <li><strong>Text alignment:</strong> Input text and placeholder text automatically right-align in RTL mode.</li>
            <li><strong>Helper row:</strong> Helper text starts from the right, counter moves to the left.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

